Personal Website
================

It is created with mostly html, css and js.

The project runs directly on the browser (any decent modern browser) without any special configurations.

Hosting
=======

The website is hosted on github pages.
Github assigns a free domain to each user.
This can be used to deploy static websites like this site.

The website url is at <https://gekkowrld.github.io/personal_website>

Disclaimer
==========

This website is not optimized for small devices (less than 830px)
